	(93,'转发项目进程：泽姐“清明放假前的唠叨唠叨”','<span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:23px;\"><span>Dear sifer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连续一个星期的会议，我们这群人越来越有发疯的劲儿了，</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">而团队未来的希望就在这种疯狂中日渐清晰明显，</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我们的工作就是把北师赛扶的每一步辛苦付出像拼图一样拼起来</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这是一份充满挑战的工作，而我们，就是为了迎接挑战而生！</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">回想这一个星期的工作。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我们对整个</span><span>presentation</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">达成了宏观认识：</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开头项目概括视频</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">蚝壳项目</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">绿道项目</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">其他项目</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">团队文化视频</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我们梳理了项目</span><span>presentation</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的大框架：</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">项目背景，分析问题，项目实施，项目成果，未来规划，五大标准。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我们了解了整个蚝壳项目的运营情况。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">而昨晚我们用三个小时对蚝壳项目进行了具体整理</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">稍后雪珂会发给大家</span><span><br />\n6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号回来，希望用</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天时间对今晚的讨论结果进行细节补充。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">而这一部分涉及到各种商业知识，</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">今晚，我们用各种朴实的语言把事情捋顺出来了。现在缺的是一些华丽丽的商业名词。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">例如</span><span>SWOT</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这种被各个团队用烂了的东西，我们一定会想出更好的！！</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">接下来四天，让我们好好放松下心情。整理下思绪。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">拿出书本，带着这些问题去重视它们，我相信大家会有更多感悟的。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这里跟大家预告下本月日程安排，</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">红色为讨论组。橘黄色为</span><span>presenter+ppt</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">组。蓝色为视频组。绿色为</span><span>AR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。紫色为团队简介。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人员分工仍按第一次开会结果。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">第一阶段：蚝壳项目</span><span style=\"color:red;\"><br />\n31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号了解项目</span><span style=\"color:red;\"><br />\n1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号整理</span><span style=\"color:red;\">&nbsp;</span><span><br />\n2—5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号清明放假</span><span>&nbsp;<br />\n<span style=\"color:red;\">6</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号细节整理、修改</span><span style=\"color:red;\">&nbsp;</span><span><br />\n<span style=\"color:red;\">7</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号问老师意见</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#ff6600;\"><br />\n8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号初稿完成</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">制作中文</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">ppt<br />\n9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">-10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号学生翻译</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\"><br />\n11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号老师修改</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">第二阶段：其他。</span><span><br />\n<span style=\"color:red;\">7</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号讨论开场项目概括视频、团队文化视频</span><span style=\"color:red;\"><br />\n</span><span><span style=\"color:blue;\">7-14</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:blue;\">号制作视频</span><span style=\"color:blue;\"><br />\n</span><span style=\"color:red;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号了解绿道项目</span><span style=\"color:red;\"><br />\n9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号（星期六）一天搞定绿道</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff9900;\">写稿</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">制作</span><span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">ppt</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:red;\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号（星期天）了解整理其他项目、开头结尾</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">写稿</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">制作</span><span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">ppt</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:red;\">11</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;\">号询问老师意见</span><span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#ff6600;\">12</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号修改稿（中文）</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\"><br />\n13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号学生翻译</span><span style=\"color:#ff6600;\"><br />\n14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff6600;\">号老师修改</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"color:blue;\"><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#339966;\">由于</span><span style=\"color:#339966;\">AR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#339966;\">与</span><span style=\"color:#339966;\">ppt</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#339966;\">契合度很高，所以不用急，等</span><span style=\"color:#339966;\">ppt</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#339966;\">出</span><span style=\"color:#339966;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#339966;\">来，简单排版即可。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#cc99ff;\">团队简介</span><span style=\"color:#cc99ff;\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#cc99ff;\">号前搞定。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">第三阶段：整合</span><span><br />\n15—23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号，所有一切搞定。</span><span>Pre</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，</span><span>ppt</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，</span><span>VCR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，年报，</span><span>Q&amp;A<br />\n24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号，放松</span><span><br />\n25-27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号，各种熟能生巧</span><span><br />\n28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">比赛</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">为节省大家时间，每次开会不用备赛组全员到，收到短信的</span><span>sifer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">出席即可。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">涉及到具体分工时，大家再具体落实各自负责部分。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">好了，唠叨完了。各位工作狂，清明假期无论多忙，最少都要找出一天时间给自己好好放松下。</span><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对自己好点！</span><span><br />\nhave a nice day~</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">！</span></span>','group',82862,43851,NULL,NULL,'2011-04-02 18:33:18','2011-04-02 19:36:40',10,NULL,NULL),
